<h1>Our Stats</h1>
<h3><%= @topic.name %></h3> Rating: <%= pluralize(@topic.average_rating, "star") %>  on average by our users.</br>
appeared <%= @topic.percentage %>% of total conversations. 


<h1>Your Ratings</h1>

<p>You have had <%= pluralize(current_user.topic_count(@topic), "conversation") %> about <%= @topic.name %>.</p>

<p>In <%= current_user.topic_count_for(@topic).round(2) %> percent of your conversations, you talked about <%= @topic.name %>.</p>

<p>on average a conversation where you talked about <%= @topic.name %> was rated: 

  <%= current_user.average_rating_for_topic(@topic)%> </p> 



<p>You talked about <%= @topic.name %> with: </p>
<ul>
  <% current_user.all_partners_with(@topic).each do |partner| %>
    <li>
    <%= link_to partner.name, partner_path(partner) %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>



<p>Conversation List involoved in this topic </p>
<ul>
<% current_user.conversations_about_topic(@topic).each do |convo| %>
<li> <%= link_to convo.time.to_date, conversation_path(convo) %> </li>
<% end %> 
</ul>
</br>

<%= link_to "All Topics",  topics_path %></br></br>
<%= link_to "Back to my my homepage", user_path(current_user) %>